{
  "stem": "27509.9",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was in history, and philosophy, and in the whatever else was the other-- the third subject.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the history lecturer told me, don't stay here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Take your results and go to Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They will accept you now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They grabbed me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They saw my paper, they saw my results.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I've done-- I've done an honors course at Melbourne and wrote a major work in-- in Jewish-- in Hebrew literature.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was-- my work in the honors course was on the subject of the relative relevance of [NON-ENGLISH] to Jew in our time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was a very well-received paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I finished it, I went-- at that time, Professor [NON-ENGLISH], if you remember that name-- he was a Japanese professor who came here, took over the Department of Middle Eastern Studies at Melbourne University-- just came and took over.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I came to see him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was a linguist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was not a professor of Judaica in the full sense, a gamut of all-- he was a linguist.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I came, I said to him, I want to continue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I've done my-- my honors degree.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I want to continue and do a master's.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, yes, do so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I suggest to you that I've-- that as you have written your honors thesis on the [NON-ENGLISH], and you came to such a conclusion-- and my conclusion was that [NON-ENGLISH] is, today, more relevant than [NON-ENGLISH] to Jew in our time.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, why don't you continue with that thought and develop that thought?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Go home and think of a subject, of a topic, and come back to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said to him, would you mind if I will throw out a subject right away?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't prepared for that suggestion.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
